oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: TS meter
zinc sulphate turbidity test

oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Panel discussion about using a TS meter to check serum protein as a comparison against the zinc sulphate turbidity test, what disinfectants or type of chemicals can be used to disinfect equipment that is being used on multiple animals, use of vaccine to keep herds intact, culling procedure of the herds in Europe, importance of insect vectors, percent of fetal calves developing lymphosarcoma.
